summary: expect to see a lot of Marvel stuff here
title: expect to see a lot of Marvel stuff here
body:
AAAAH LET ME TELL YOU A STORY

I watched like Iron Man , Thor and only one Avengers when I was a teen. I never been a fan. AND in April this year , as my son is 120% in love with Captain America , I took him to Disneyland Paris to meet Captain. It was just one of my most wonderful memory at Disney , he run right into his arms , his eyes literally SPARKLED , and after this we got to see an Avengers show in Disney Studio.  

I wasn’t really excited at first because Marvel , Avengers was just…Meh to me. I don’t liked it this much. And the show was AMAZING , the effects was incredible! And at one moment in the show , Thanos appears in front of Black Widow , saying his gonna destroy all super heroes , and Natasha tell him “ You can destroy us , all of us , but I know , there’s always be a lonely girl or a shy boy , ready to transform themself and fight for what is good “

And oh boy this line just hit me like an arrow in the heart. Like I suddently realized what being a Superhero mean , and then at the end Cap just screaming AVENGERS ASSEMBLE ! AND I CRIED ALTHOUGH I’VE NEVER SEEN ONE FREAKING MOVIE and when the show ended , I was with my two sisters who is marvel’s fan since the first Iron Man , and I said “ This show just broke me. as soon as we got home , I want to see ALL THE MOVIES “ 

AAAnnnnddd that’s how I see all the MCU Movies in like 2 or 3 weeks for being ready to seeing Endgame ! 

And God I’m so grateful , I feel like a discovered something amazing , I’ve honestly haven’t been so in love with something since Stranger Things ♥
